+256 |  0x101    0x103    0x105    0x107     0x???   
+32k |  0x110    0x113    0x116    0x119     0x173   
+64k |  0x111    0x114    0x117    0x11A     0x174   
+16M |  0x112    0x115    0x118    0x11B     0x175   
 
 The video mode number of the Linux kernel is the VESA mode number plus
 0x200.
